ast.name: Ship Defender
ast.comment:
Shoot the enemies!
There is a boss every 300 points.
Tap/drag on the left side of the screen to move.
Tap anywhere on the screen to shoot.
Keep the orientation in landscape.
Try for a high score! (Leaderboard not enabled)

body.text: The board is a 2D canvas with a physics engine. Gravity makes sprites fall and boundary makes them bounce.
